Function Sources & Project Info:
-----------------------------
File types and meaning:
.a Final C version of a function ready
  for assembly by assm in to a .o file.

.asm TMP Version in SEQ format for 
  testing modifications. This version
  will be different than the finished
  .a version.

.o Object file to link in to your C
  programs.

.c Usually a file to test the ML
  function with.


